lead_paragraph: South Korea's Eun Jeong Seong and Italy's Virginia Elena Carta each won two matches Thursday in the U.S. Women's Amateur to keep alive their bids for rare season sweeps.

headline.print_headline: Seong, Carta Advance in US Women's Amateur at Rolling Green
